Q_DESC:
Write a program which takes input as string and then implement the logic to find out Consonants, Digits, White spaces and Vowels in string

Refer sample input and output:

Input 1:
SRM University 600203
Output 1:
Vowels:4
Consonants:10
Whitespaces:3
Digits:6

india won the world cup during 1983 and 2011

Whitespaces:8
Digits:8

WELCOME TO ELAB AUTO EVALUATION TOOL 2017

Consonants:14
Whitespaces:6
Digits:4
